Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老師\N（98堂 Yamete 精準提取）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你又穿著睡衣出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最近剛剛測試完， 要改卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還要整理各種數據
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多事情忙到很晚才睡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,另外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,「老師」這個稱呼你也差不多該換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓我像是在學校一樣，很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,總是不自覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老師就是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里你也不是我的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,而是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-那，吃飯吧。   -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫眼前的侵犯\N被重複的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月朱里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi，這裡是榎本家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,5年沒有聽到的聲音，還是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,您是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聖火女子高中，3年1班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,榎本 朱里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不，舊姓 彩月朱里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你那晶瑩剔透的潔白的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,柔軟的雙唇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,像天使一樣的你，一點也不相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些通過下體肉壁 流淌進去的男性精子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即使現在 仍在疼痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那些被凌辱過後的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我體內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不潔的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,凌辱的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來送包裹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,否則殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不許出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，我是處女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,停止，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幹到你真是太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,警察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人被送到監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,家人和附近的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,以為只是以為我被什麼襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也閉口不談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,像是回到了什麼都沒發生的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,被撕裂身體和心靈的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想到了死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月，你身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老師會讓你忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,當時，擔任社團顧問的 現在的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,榎本先生拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在接近畢業的時候，接受了他的求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在他不變的溫柔關懷下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了不潔的記憶 和被凌辱的刻印的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你那晶瑩剔透的潔白的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,柔軟的雙唇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,像天使一樣的你，一點也不相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那些通過下體肉壁流淌進去的男性精子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是哪裡出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙應該不可能認識如今的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,應該還在監獄裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以先睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，剛才你說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚也通宵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，明天講課要用的講義，還有一些報告之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好像還挺花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎，那注意身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安\N-晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是丈夫最終的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想成為他的絆腳石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不振作起來不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-路上小心\N-我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少女的香味消失了，卻有了成熟女人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,時間的流逝真是無情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這個瞬間，你知道 我等了多久嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,從少女變成女人的這五年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要好好地讓我享受一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為我為什麼會無償的 忍耐那麼長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在那個無聊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一個是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,另一個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是長成大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說過了別大聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,和那個時候我說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的丈夫是學校的老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,現在應該會很苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能會不抱怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子被強暴，而且被同一個男人強暴兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真成問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不想被你丈夫知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,記起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會好好疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是長成大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快點，脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你想清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:20:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,被丈夫知道的話你會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定是最不想讓他知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒楣被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,現在再也不會失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定還是會被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,味道很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.25,0:25:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.19,0:25:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.79,0:25:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,被丈夫知道了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.60,0:25:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還是兩次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.67,0:25:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被同一個男人幹的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.00,0:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,作為男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.95,0:25:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.16,0:25:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就不會有人知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.72,0:26:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯，過來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.09,0:26:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你聲音太大的話 會被鄰居知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.99,0:28:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.33,0:28:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.27,0:28:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在抽動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.67,0:28:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,即使嘴裡喊著不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.15,0:28:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,身體還是有感覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.15,0:29:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明明身體很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.07,0:29:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.74,0:30:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴已經這麼濕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.35,0:30:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.02,0:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.95,0:31:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.03,0:31:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.99,0:31:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.07,0:32:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.34,0:32:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.98,0:32:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.86,0:32:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.02,0:33:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快做
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.63,0:33:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到沒，太太
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.84,0:33:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.41,0:35:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.02,0:35:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不好好舔的話，可是不會舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.06,0:36:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,五年不見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.47,0:36:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,逃到一邊我可插不進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.77,0:38:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.31,0:38:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.53,0:38:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.96,0:39:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.37,0:39:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.71,0:39:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.31,0:39:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.68,0:40:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,站床下趴著
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.75,0:40:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.02,0:41:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖聽話別說出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.03,0:41:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,奶子比以前大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.70,0:41:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.11,0:41:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要幹我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.05,0:41:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.72,0:41:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有幹你的權力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.98,0:42:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.36,0:43:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.36,0:43:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.03,0:43:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,記清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.63,0:43:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把家裡的鎖打開
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好讓我可以隨時進來
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.98,0:43:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,像他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.65,0:43:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,重複著羞恥和屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.18,0:43:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.25,0:44:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,凌辱的地獄般的每天開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.54,0:44:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-路上小心\N-嗯，我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.07,0:44:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.41,0:44:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,從昨天開始好像都很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.95,0:44:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係，沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.75,0:44:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.62,0:44:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-那我走了哦.   -路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.60,0:45:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想試試小市民的幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.41,0:45:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫我實現我的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.88,0:45:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.43,0:45:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.85,0:46:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.52,0:46:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,淫蕩的太太當然是 裸體穿圍裙咯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.33,0:46:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.95,0:46:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.03,0:47:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快點照做
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.06,0:47:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,又能聞到味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.18,0:48:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這個不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.65,0:48:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.45,0:48:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要裸體穿圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:48:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.49,0:49:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣也脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.02,0:49:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說了裸體的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.83,0:49:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快點做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.68,0:49:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.08,0:50:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看後面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.63,0:50:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.03,0:50:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.18,0:50:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自慰給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.46,0:50:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託您了啦\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.40,0:51:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,給你準備的場所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.95,0:51:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.11,0:51:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.91,0:51:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,食物都冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.87,0:52:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來，快做
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.03,0:52:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,做啊，做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.85,0:52:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好安慰自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.58,0:52:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,現在穿的真是大膽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.86,0:53:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的太太喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.54,0:53:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,多高潮幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.88,0:53:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.22,0:53:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,畫著圈舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.83,0:53:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.55,0:54:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快點射
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.37,0:54:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.91,0:54:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,摸小穴摸到它尿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.91,0:55:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.67,0:55:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.61,0:55:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.41,0:55:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.96,0:55:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.56,0:55:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.84,0:56:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服了就尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.05,0:56:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快點尿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.75,0:56:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.08,0:57:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.88,0:57:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,用它的話會非常舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.97,0:58:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧，這邊會更舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.05,0:59:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,又舒服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.20,0:59:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尿多少次都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.60,0:59:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡淫蕩的太太了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.01,1:00:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,全部尿出來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.35,1:00:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,尿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.60,1:00:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,手動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.27,1:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.35,1:01:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的雞巴怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.76,1:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,硬不硬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.09,1:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,硬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.83,1:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大不大
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.43,1:01:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.16,1:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-涼的還是熱的？  -熱的.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.17,1:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個放到小穴裡面，會很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.05,1:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,做做看
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.06,1:01:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.46,1:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.34,1:02:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感覺一下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.97,1:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我就說想要像你這樣的淫蕩太太
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.86,1:03:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,掐死你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.86,1:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說了掐死你啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.97,1:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還是那麼容易興奮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.01,1:07:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把胳膊夾起來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.63,1:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大奶子會疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.50,1:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.97,1:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.24,1:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也疼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.25,1:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼喔
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.58,1:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是不是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.69,1:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊，疼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.10,1:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊，沒辦法忍受
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.97,1:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,別對我的奶子太粗暴
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.00,1:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.54,1:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能尿出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.35,1:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以嗎？  -不可以.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.35,1:10:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.95,1:10:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那，換個玩法
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.04,1:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真是淫蕩哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.01,1:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴又熱又濕哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.35,1:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你淫蕩的小穴很想要哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.98,1:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.52,1:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.12,1:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.66,1:11:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這麼粗暴
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.26,1:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.04,1:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴都變硬了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.98,1:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小核也變硬了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.06,1:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,站直點
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.40,1:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,手放後面
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.73,1:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.93,1:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.81,1:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.02,1:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快好了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.64,1:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,站直
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.04,1:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.18,1:13:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還真的很適合這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.03,1:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能動了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.05,1:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個解掉
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.81,1:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,解開
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.98,1:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.98,1:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.00,1:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.01,1:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有被丈夫調教過嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.08,1:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.22,1:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再吃進去點
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.96,1:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這就可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.25,1:17:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我舒服舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.00,1:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔舔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.04,1:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊已經有精液流出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.12,1:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,打掃打掃
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.25,1:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.34,1:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.47,1:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,弄乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.15,1:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不能停下哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.57,1:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不夠色情
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.17,1:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等一會
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.65,1:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就夠色情了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.97,1:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,腿立起來
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.95,1:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,聽話
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.30,1:22:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的話是不是色情了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.97,1:23:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,過來，舔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.14,1:24:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,腿夾好，可別掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.02,1:25:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi，榎本家
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.30,1:25:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老公嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.37,1:25:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我在車站，有什麼要買的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.37,1:25:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.77,1:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好，知道了.\N大概10分鐘後到家
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.44,1:26:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.12,1:26:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.86,1:26:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是要回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.93,1:26:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快點讓我射
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.93,1:26:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老公要回來了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.13,1:26:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.87,1:26:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,會被看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.14,1:26:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才說快點讓我射啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.01,1:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都會被看到哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.95,1:26:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.06,1:27:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不加油快點的話
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.40,1:27:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會被看到的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.40,1:27:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要讓我射就可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.01,1:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.34,1:27:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.88,1:27:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快讓我射
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.04,1:28:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.44,1:28:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被丈夫看到了就糟了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.98,1:28:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了，差不多要回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.07,1:28:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.08,1:28:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈點
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.59,1:29:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公要回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.72,1:29:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,把我解開
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.99,1:29:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.73,1:29:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他也看看
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.00,1:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,純潔賢淑妻子的真正模樣
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.81,1:29:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.81,1:30:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快把我解開
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.62,1:30:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，既然你丈夫要回來了，我也要回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.09,1:30:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-再見.    -等等.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.56,1:30:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個解開
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.25,1:30:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.86,1:30:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.06,1:30:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-你回來了.    -怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.26,1:30:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在洗衣服，沒有聽到
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.33,1:30:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡水現在已經放好了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.40,1:31:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒準備飯，你先慢慢洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.28,1:31:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好，知道了.\N那我先洗澡了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.08,1:31:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.16,1:31:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是又興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.03,1:31:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.43,1:31:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.17,1:31:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.71,1:31:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,越是感覺羞恥越興奮的話，就是變態
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.92,1:31:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的本性
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.45,1:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,重複著羞恥和屈辱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.92,1:31:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.99,1:31:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,凌辱的地獄般的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.33,1:32:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然而我害怕的是
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.27,1:32:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是漸漸被快樂充盈的我自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.42,1:32:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.70,1:32:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,暱稱「大天使」
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.37,1:32:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不，還是叫你榎本老師 比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.04,1:32:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.97,1:32:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,道貌岸然的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.11,1:32:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候是你報的警吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.45,1:32:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.58,1:32:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.98,1:32:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你卻得到了自己喜歡的天使
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.52,1:32:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在也變得很漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.12,1:33:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.39,1:33:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,難道對朱里出手了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.26,1:33:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果對朱莉出手的話，我會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.67,1:33:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不應該說這種話
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.34,1:33:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠我的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.01,1:33:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你太太說好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.55,1:33:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.82,1:33:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.89,1:33:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那能不能仔細說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.56,1:33:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你的懺悔
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.97,1:33:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.84,1:33:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.44,1:33:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.18,1:33:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最近有沒有奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.78,1:33:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比如說
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.92,1:33:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有奇怪的男人來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.19,1:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.52,1:34:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.46,1:34:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼，沒有就好
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.13,1:34:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是這附近有奇怪的人出現
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.73,1:34:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,警察有聯絡學校
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.07,1:34:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.20,1:34:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.21,1:34:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我這樣 也是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.28,1:34:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.99,1:35:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.13,1:35:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和你的丈夫見面了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.00,1:35:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.40,1:35:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.94,1:35:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有說我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.21,1:35:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.68,1:35:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在監獄中忍耐的理由，有兩個
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.55,1:35:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一個是你
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.29,1:35:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,另一個還沒有說 ，對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.02,1:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說的話還需要另一個人物 登場
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.31,1:36:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再深點
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.01,1:36:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,坐深點
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.25,1:37:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.59,1:37:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.05,1:37:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.53,1:37:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.26,1:37:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.00,1:37:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.09,1:37:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你得到手的人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.02,1:37:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,天使的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.43,1:38:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.23,1:38:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.64,1:38:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,還有更精彩的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.74,1:38:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.07,1:38:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這淫蕩的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.01,1:38:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.56,1:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看著哦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.97,1:39:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.84,1:39:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前的那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.65,1:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是受你丈夫指使的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.05,1:39:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.06,1:39:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是在網絡上認識的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.33,1:39:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.53,1:39:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想要得到某個高中女生
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.87,1:39:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.41,1:39:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,身心都如天使的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.41,1:40:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他是一個連話都不敢跟她講的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.89,1:40:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是差勁的人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.75,1:40:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,首先讓我強暴你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.36,1:40:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,裝著安慰受傷的你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.56,1:40:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,接近你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.97,1:40:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然後慢慢用手段使你成為他的人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.58,1:40:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊， 那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.51,1:40:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.38,1:40:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.13,1:40:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.26,1:40:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你看下證據吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.40,1:40:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你所信任的最溫柔的老師
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.54,1:41:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫的告白
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.34,1:41:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能仔細說給我聽，你的懺悔
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.82,1:41:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.08,1:41:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.95,1:41:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了朱里
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.29,1:41:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要她
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.04,1:41:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.40,1:41:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了，你是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.67,1:42:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.27,1:42:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會放開你的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.41,1:42:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都操你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.69,1:42:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.30,1:42:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.58,1:42:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.65,1:42:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.39,1:42:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了這個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.19,1:42:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,才在監獄裡老老實實待了五年的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.66,1:43:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為了這個時候
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.00,1:43:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.67,1:43:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.41,1:43:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.35,1:43:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不放開你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.41,1:43:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要幹你一輩子
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.27,1:44:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.34,1:44:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在你老公的面前
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.81,1:44:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,被我這麼操
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.41,1:44:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.21,1:45:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.28,1:45:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,心愛的妻子被人在眼前上的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.88,1:45:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,反正她也不是你能掌握的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.39,1:46:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你這輩子都不能從我身邊逃開！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.08,1:47:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你這輩子都不能從我身邊逃開！
